OL,3,CRat-infested restaurant fined
OL,4,Cthousands for food safety breaches
OL,6,FA rat-infested restaurant in Cornwall
OL,7,Fhas been fined nearly #5,000 after a
OL,8,Fvisit from the environmental health
OL,9,Finspector.
OL,11,FThe conditions at 12 Beach Road in
OL,12,FNewquay were described as "filthy" and
OL,13,Fcovered in rat poo.
OL,15,FA live rodent was even spotted in the
OL,16,Fcorridor while they were there.
OL,18,FPollocks Pub Company Ltd has pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty at Bodmin Magistrates' Court to
OL,20,Fthree offences under food hygiene
OL,21,Fregulations.
