OL,3,CRat-infested restaurant fined
OL,4,Cthousands for food safety breaches
OL,6,FMagistrates heard of the conditions
OL,7,Fthat were found that following an
OL,8,Finspection on 18 October, 2023.
OL,10,FThe inspecting officer found filthy
OL,11,Fconditions, an active rat infestation,
OL,12,Fand a clear failure to implement
OL,13,Fsystems to ensure safe food was served
OL,14,Fto their customers.
OL,16,FFood equipment and the structure of
OL,17,Fthe premises was found to be in a poor
OL,18,Fstate of cleanliness with significant
OL,19,Fdirt observed.
