OL,3,CRat-infested restaurant fined
OL,4,Cthousands for food safety breaches
OL,6,FThere was an extensive rodent
OL,7,Finfestation and activity throughout
OL,8,Fthe building.
OL,10,FLarge amounts of both old and fresh
OL,11,Frodent droppings were observed in
OL,12,Fareas used for food and drink storage
OL,13,Fand preparation.
OL,15,FA live rat was seen in the corridor
OL,16,Fadjoining the kitchen by the officer
OL,17,Fat the time of the inspection.
