OL,3,CRat-infested restaurant fined
OL,4,Cthousands for food safety breaches
OL,6,FFollowing the inspection last year,
OL,7,Fthey agreed to voluntarily close the
OL,8,Fpremises whilst the infestation was
OL,9,Fdealt with and to undertake a deep
OL,10,Fclean.
OL,12,FFurther investigation indicated that
OL,13,Fthere had been an ongoing rodent
OL,14,Finfestation at the premises for some
OL,15,Ftime, during which they continued to
OL,16,Ftrade, putting their customers at risk.
