OL,3,CRat-infested restaurant fined
OL,4,Cthousands for food safety breaches
OL,6,FPollocks Pub Company Ltd, which
OL,7,Foperate a number of restaurants and
OL,8,Fbars in Cornwall, was fined #1,000
OL,9,Fwith an additional victim surcharge of
OL,10,F#400 and the Council was awarded costs
OL,11,Fof #3,426.
OL,13,FSumming up, the Magistrates said these
OL,14,Fwere serious breaches of the
OL,15,Fregulations that potentially put the
OL,16,Fpublic at risk, and that food ratings
OL,17,Fwere earned and not entitled.
