OL,6,FCouncillor Martyn Alvey, portfolio
OL,7,Fholder responsible for Enforcement and
OL,8,FPublic Protection at Cornwall Council,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Clearly the conditions at these
OL,10,Fpremises were far below the required
OL,11,Fstandard. This business knew it had a
OL,12,Frodent problem but failed to address
OL,13,Fit.
OL,15,F"I hope this case acts a reminder to
OL,16,Fother food businesses that we will not
OL,17,Fhesitate to prosecute where members of
OL,18,Fthe public are put at risk in this
OL,19,Fway."
